Zero point energy                ...      0.05237072 Eh      32.86 kcal/mol
Thermal vibrational correction   ...      0.00044688 Eh       0.28 kcal/mol
Thermal rotational correction    ...      0.00141627 Eh       0.89 kcal/mol
